  <section class='section alt' id='promo'>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='hero-unit'>
        <h1>What is CD Kickstart?</h1>
        <p>
          In two days, we'll teach you everything you need to be off and running with Continuous Delivery.
        </p>

        <p>
          We'll start by teaching you the fundamental principles</a> of Continuous Delivery, and how it fits
          into the wider world of agile. We'll show you how integrate a set of tools to create a deployment pipeline allowing your code to flow smoothly though all the stages from development to production.
        </p>

        <p>
          Then we'll investigate how having this pipeline allows us to deploy code in much smaller batch sizes, iterating more quickly. We'll look at how automating the integration, test and release processes can change the way that a development team behaves, and the way we think about developing new features.  
        </p>

        <p>
          Read further for <a href='#learningoutcomes'>full details of our learning outcomes</a>. The course is practical and you'll experience putting the tools into action, as well as getting the theory behind them.</p>
      </div>
      <div class='hero-unit pull-left'>
        <h2>
          <a class="btn btn-primary btn-large" href="/dates#<%= events.first.id %>">Book CD Kickstart</a>
          <small>Next date: <%= course_date_range(events.first.full_date) %>, <%= events.first.title %></small>
        </h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section class='section alt' id="applied">
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='page-header'>
        <h1>
          Continuous Delivery
          <small>Two-day technical workshop for developers, operations people and project managers.</small>
        </h1>
      </div>
      <div class='row-fluid'>
        <ul class='thumbnails bordered'>
          <li class='span6'>
